  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of CBT-001 Ophthalmic Solution in Patients With Pterygium</brief_title>
  <acronym>Pterygium</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 2a Multicenter, Randomized, Vehicle-Controlled, Dose Escalating Study to Evaluate the Safety, Efficacy and Pharmacokinetics of CBT-001 Ophthalmic Solution in Patients With Primary or Recurrent Pterygium</official_title>
